01:28:22,039 --> 01:28:26,319
[SPEAKER_00] Ma ti sam, to je u podlozi uvijek strah da će nešto završiti.

1213
01:28:26,319 --> 01:28:27,140
[SPEAKER_00] Doći će kraj.

1214
01:28:27,300 --> 01:28:30,220
[SPEAKER_00] Kraj dolazi i svi smo u tom vlaku bez niznimka.

1215
01:28:30,220 --> 01:28:33,140
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam tu malo ekstremno.

1216
01:28:33,140 --> 01:28:35,300
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ja sam, malo ekstremno.

1217
01:28:35,300 --> 01:28:38,439
[SPEAKER_00] Kad se moj sin rodio, ja sam se toliko,

1218
01:28:38,439 --> 01:28:43,800
[SPEAKER_00] ko prva sva što ti kažeš, nevjerojatno je da onaj video si snimio.

1219
01:28:43,800 --> 01:28:46,239
[SPEAKER_00] Meni je nevjerojatno prvo da avion poleti u zraku,

1220
01:28:46,239 --> 01:28:48,859
[SPEAKER_00] ja i dalje ne mogu to činje, co prihvatiti, to mi je nevjerojatno.

1221
01:28:48,859 --> 01:28:50,979
[SPEAKER_00] A drugo je da je ljudsko biće izašlo iz mene.

1222
01:28:50,979 --> 01:28:52,619
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, what?

1223
01:28:52,619 --> 01:28:53,920
[SPEAKER_00] What?

1224
01:28:53,920 --> 01:28:55,220
[SPEAKER_00] Razumiješ?

1225
01:28:55,939 --> 01:28:58,340
[SPEAKER_00] I sad to ljudsko biće diše, ima mišljenje,

1226
01:28:58,340 --> 01:29:00,720
[SPEAKER_00] ti si odgovoran za njega do 80 godina

1227
01:29:00,720 --> 01:29:03,479
[SPEAKER_00] i onda ja jednog dana shvatim i on će umret.

1228
01:29:03,479 --> 01:29:09,399
[SPEAKER_00] Ej, znači ono, čak se malo, ma ne, ne, pa kako ću sad?

1229
01:29:09,399 --> 01:29:11,800
[SPEAKER_00] Kontrola, strah, strah, opet od smrti.

1230
01:29:11,800 --> 01:29:15,359
[SPEAKER_00] Ja moram iskontrolirat sve da to bude onako lijepo,

1231
01:29:15,359 --> 01:29:18,260
[SPEAKER_00] pa da, svi to mi znamo ko neku priču, umriću jednog dana.

1232
01:29:18,260 --> 01:29:21,460
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, ja kad sam ležala poluparalizirana

1233
01:29:21,460 --> 01:29:23,800
[SPEAKER_00] i nisam imala društveni život, ni dečka,

1234
01:29:24,460 --> 01:29:27,180
[SPEAKER_00] nisam opće dejtala 10 godina, to je bilo sve nešto,

1235
01:29:27,180 --> 01:29:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] ono, nekakvi random ljudi, ako sam isretala, ležala doma.

1236
01:29:31,000 --> 01:29:34,180
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam bila depresivna i suicidalna misli sam imala.

1237
01:29:35,399 --> 01:29:40,039
[SPEAKER_00] i nakon potresa mi se desilo kao, ono, sad će se sve srušiti,

1238
01:29:40,039 --> 01:29:42,939
[SPEAKER_00] znači ono, zanimljeno, još uz ovu moju maštu koju ja imam,

1239
01:29:42,939 --> 01:29:46,760
[SPEAKER_00] sve moguće crne scenarije sam odradila u glavi,

1240
01:29:46,760 --> 01:29:50,520
[SPEAKER_00] i onda sam skužila jednog dana, sam me rekao,

1241
01:29:50,520 --> 01:29:54,199
[SPEAKER_00] a znači šta, dobro, ajde, ajde, drvni,

1242
01:29:54,199 --> 01:29:58,560
[SPEAKER_00] i ja da umrem, onako nekako, stojički sam nekako krenula,

1243
01:29:58,560 --> 01:30:02,520
[SPEAKER_00] i onda sam se smirila, vratila sam fokus na dah

1244
01:30:02,520 --> 01:30:04,420
[SPEAKER_00] i rekao sam, uđi u moje srce.

1245
01:30:04,420 --> 01:30:10,140
[SPEAKER_00] I, referenca na Matrix, kada gen skoči u njega,

1246
01:30:10,140 --> 01:30:12,180
[SPEAKER_00] ja to kažem da je to, ok?

1247
01:30:12,180 --> 01:30:16,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ti si dozvolio, prihvatio si i taj naboj,

1248
01:30:16,539 --> 01:30:20,159
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam usjetila kako se ja širim,

1249
01:30:20,159 --> 01:30:24,640
[SPEAKER_00] i došao te neke balanse,

1250
01:30:24,640 --> 01:30:26,380
[SPEAKER_00] jednom onako otvorim oči, skužim,

1251
01:30:26,560 --> 01:30:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] da se nisam bojala ako prije tri sekunde.

1252
01:30:29,000 --> 01:30:32,180
[SPEAKER_00] Čekaj malo, to sam ja napravila.

1253
01:30:32,180 --> 01:30:36,380
[SPEAKER_00] I onda sa tim zamišljanjima, tim scenarijima,

1254
01:30:36,380 --> 01:30:39,260
[SPEAKER_00] i, pazi, to nije nešto sam ja obavila uptidu,

1255
01:30:39,260 --> 01:30:41,420
[SPEAKER_00] idem živjeti svoj 3D život dalje.

1256
01:30:41,420 --> 01:30:44,079
[SPEAKER_00] To je svakodnevni posao, to je kopranje zubi, tuširanje.

1257
01:30:44,079 --> 01:30:46,739
[SPEAKER_00] Svakodnevno se ja pomislim,

1258
01:30:46,739 --> 01:30:48,340
[SPEAKER_00] ovom će sve mu doći kraj, aha.

1259
01:30:48,340 --> 01:30:50,779
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ja znam da kad dođe taj kraj,

1260
01:30:50,779 --> 01:30:53,140
[SPEAKER_00] ja ću pomisliti, ah, još samo jedan zala sunca,

1261
01:30:53,140 --> 01:30:54,439
[SPEAKER_00] još samo jedna kava,

1262
01:30:55,180 --> 01:30:56,800
[SPEAKER_00] s mlijekom, topla, turska,

1263
01:30:56,800 --> 01:30:58,319
[SPEAKER_00] još samo jedan desert,

1264
01:30:58,319 --> 01:31:01,359
[SPEAKER_00] to će doći,

1265
01:31:01,359 --> 01:31:03,539
[SPEAKER_00] i onda to obavi prije nego što dođe.

1266
01:31:03,539 --> 01:31:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sve to napravi prije nego što dođe.

1267
01:31:07,000 --> 01:31:08,739
[SPEAKER_00] Da, u trenu kad dođe,

1268
01:31:08,739 --> 01:31:10,659
[SPEAKER_00] ti znaš da si sve

1269
