[SPEAKER_00] Pazi, to je užasno teško zamisliti nekome.

1271
01:31:19,640 --> 01:31:21,380
[SPEAKER_00] Jer svi kad zamišljaju u moment smrti,

1272
01:31:21,380 --> 01:31:23,140
[SPEAKER_00] zamišljaju jesam li sve napravio,

1273
01:31:23,140 --> 01:31:25,079
