[SPEAKER_00] svi osjećaju manje više.

1275
01:31:26,920 --> 01:31:29,100
[SPEAKER_00] Ajme reći na zapadu, opet na istoku nije tako.

1276
01:31:29,100 --> 01:31:31,020
[SPEAKER_00] Osjeća se tuga, žaljenje i tako dalje.

1277
01:31:32,199 --> 01:31:33,939
[SPEAKER_00] A da si kažeš nekom ovdje sa zapada,

1278
01:31:33,939 --> 01:31:35,460
[SPEAKER_00] kad ćeš u momentu kad ćeš umirat,

1279
01:31:35,460 --> 01:31:36,239
[SPEAKER_00] budi sretan,

1280
01:31:36,239 --> 01:31:40,460
[SPEAKER_00] misle on, pa to nije normalno.

1281
01:31:40,460 --> 01:31:43,159
[SPEAKER_00] Ko kaže da to nije normalno?

1282
01:31:43,159 --> 01:31:45,439
[SPEAKER_00] Ko kaže da ne možeš otići

1283
01:31:45,439 --> 01:31:47,840
