1284
01:31:47,840 --> 01:31:49,899
[SPEAKER_00] Nećeš ti ponijeti Maja Ozić,

1285
01:31:49,899 --> 01:31:51,640
[SPEAKER_00] menadžer, umjetnik,

1286
01:31:51,640 --> 01:31:53,380
[SPEAKER_00] direktorica Bove, mama, sve.

1287
01:31:53,380 --> 01:31:54,619
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje ćeš to ponijeti?

1288
01:31:54,619 --> 01:31:56,359
[SPEAKER_00] To nećeš ponijeti.

1289
01:31:56,359 --> 01:31:59,060
[SPEAKER_00] I zato ja to, kažem, to gubljenje

1290
01:31:59,060 --> 01:32:01,340
[SPEAKER_00] svega toga, da u trenu smrti

1291
01:32:01,340 --> 01:32:03,300
[SPEAKER_00] i ništa ne ponesem sa sobom je za mene

1292
01:32:03,300 --> 01:32:06,300
[SPEAKER_00] najveća motivacija koja postoji.

1293
01:32:06,300 --> 01:32:08,159
[SPEAKER_00] Plus, pazi, deset godina, dvadesete

1294
